Sheckley, Robert. THE ROBERT SHECKLEY OMNIBUS. London: Victor Gollancz Ltd, 1973. Octavo, boards. First edition. Collects twelve stories and the novel IMMORTALITY, INC. (Anatomy of Wonder [1995] 3-157). Edited with introduction by Robert Conquest. A fine copy in fine dust jacket. (#91615).

Price: $100.00
